${offset 32}${color1}CPU  : ${color2}${top name 5}${goto 230}${color1}  ${top pid 5}${alignr}${top cpu 3}%
${offset 32}${color1}RAM  : ${color2}${top_mem name 1}${goto 230}${color1}  ${top_mem pid 1}${alignr}${top_mem mem 1}%
